interofficeMemorandum.subject: SFA CO-LEVEL Q&A FOR TEST PRODUCT
interofficeMemorandum.body:
Attached is the Q&A sheet public relations will use to respond to media enquiries concerning the co level of spA test product.

If you have any questions, please let me know.
